This kit was made to help people put together icons that are consistant with the Ubuntu
phone suru design language. It comes with paper textures and paper folds for easy uses.
Please look at the Ubuntu phone design guidelines. Url at the top. Feel free to report
issues or contribute to the kit at https://github.com/halfsail/Ubuntu-UI-Tookit
